distro.setup:
#!/bin/bash
set -o errexit
set -o verbose

umount /mnt || true
umount /dev/xvdd || true
/sbin/mkfs.xfs -f /dev/xvdd
mkdir -p /data
echo "/dev/xvdd /data auto noatime 0 0" | tee -a /etc/fstab
mount /data


chown -R ubuntu:ubuntu /data

echo "github.com,207.97.227.239 ssh-rsa " | tee -a /home/ubuntu/.ssh/known_hosts
echo "${github_private_key}" | tee /home/ubuntu/.ssh/id_rsa
echo "${github_public_key}" | tee /home/ubuntu/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
chmod 600 /home/ubuntu/.ssh/*
chown -R ubuntu:ubuntu /data
chown -R ubuntu:ubuntu /home/ubuntu/.ssh

# /tmp will be a symlink to this
#
mkdir /data/tmp
chmod 1777 /data/tmp
mkdir -p /data/var/lib/docker
systemctl restart docker

#!/bin/bash

echo "${github_private_key}" | tee /home/admin/.ssh/id_rsa
